sequenceDiagram
    %% COMP370 Mini Project 2 - Sequence: Client Request (During Failover, Bhupinder Branch)
    autonumber
    participant G as GUI
    participant M as Monitor
    participant C as Client
    participant OL as Old Leader
    participant F1 as Follower 1
    participant F2 as Follower 2
    participant NL as New Leader

    G->>M: sendRequest(command)
    M->>C: sendRequest(command)
    C->>OL: PROCESS_JOB(command)
    Note over OL: Old leader crashes or becomes unreachable
    OL--x C: socket error / timeout
    C->>C: clear cached currentLeaderId
    C-->>M: return ERROR message
    M-->>G: response string

    G->>M: discoverLeaderOnceAndNotify()

    Note over F1,F2: Remaining servers detect missing heartbeats
    F1->>F1: election timeout expires
    F1->>F1: startElection()\nbecome CANDIDATE, self-vote
    F1->>F2: RequestVoteArgs(term, candidateId, lastLogIndex, lastLogTerm)
    F2->>F2: handleRequestVote(args)
    F2-->>F1: RequestVoteResults(term, voteGranted=true)
    F1->>F1: handleVoteResult(res)\nmajority reached
    F1->>F1: becomeLeader()
    Note over F1: New leader elected

    M->>C: discoverLeader()
    C->>F2: GET_LEADER
    F2-->>C: ClientResponse(success=true, leaderId=null)
    C->>NL: GET_LEADER
    NL-->>C: ClientResponse(success=true, leaderId=NL)
    M-->>G: update("CLIENT_CONNECTED:NL") or update("LEADER_CHANGED:NL")

    Note over G: User can resend command after reconnection
